com.scg.util

Class ListFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scg.util.ListFactory

  • public final class ListFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Generates a set of test data for testing purposes. Time cards are generated in both February and March, the end of February/beginning of March occurs mid week, so time cards may have time on them from both months. The year used for the test data is available in the TEST_YEAR static member.
